  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0d82\u0da2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dab \u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dc4\u0dc3 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Give Ranjan full freedom",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the leader of the opposition, said that he expects that Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake, who is the expectation of everyone, will get full freedom and is waiting for that day.",
        "The opposition leader said that it is his sole objective to see Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake, who has continued popularity as a philanthropic politician as well as a folk artist, come back to the society as a free citizen and work energetically for social justice.",
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the opposition leader, who went to the Welikada prison to check on the well-being of Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake, who is incarcerated in the Welikada prison, said this while speaking to the media.",
        "The opposition leader also exchanged views with Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake there for a long time."
      ],
